SIMPLE: superfine
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superfine
<hw>Su"per*fine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Very
fine, or most fine; being of surpassing fineness; of extra nice or fine
quality; <as>as, <ex>superfine</ex> cloth</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Excessively fine; too nice; over particular; <as>as,
<ex>superfine</ex> distinctions; <ex>superfine</ex>
tastes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superfineness</ent>⟦br⟧
